er.com/sera_alb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">濑良阿尔巴</a>、宇<a href="https://twitter.com/uno_kgs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">野加濑</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/otoha_ks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">乙羽喀什</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/itsuki_htsr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">五木人四郎</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/nanamona_mr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">七名丸</a>。</p><p>此外，VEE官方YouTube频道还公开了纪念转会和加盟的PV。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[VEE] VERSEⁿ 人才转会公告PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UaevK6USt3M?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000120.000049041.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">索尼音乐娱乐公司新闻稿</a></p><h2>《二十三寺通勤·学校之声》、《二十三寺共享之家之声》即将发售</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/61b9bcb8b7b210285530bc5fce4d08c4-kix.5ekaqc8ww1nh-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/61b9bcb8b7b210285530bc5fce4d08c4-kix.5ekaqc8ww1nh-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/61b9bcb8b7b210285530bc5fce4d08c4-kix.5ekaqc8ww1nh-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/61b9bcb8b7b210285530bc5fce4d08c4-kix.5ekaqc8ww1nh-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/61b9bcb8b7b210285530bc5fce4d08c4-kix.5ekaqc8ww1nh-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/61b9bcb8b7b210285530bc5fce4d08c4-kix.5ekaqc8ww1nh-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/61b9bcb8b7b210285530bc5fce4d08c4-kix.5ekaqc8ww1nh-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://twitter.com/nijisanji_app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a>将于4月8日星期一12:00起在Nijisan