ber 为人气游戏贡献了部分人气的话题经常升温。看来Vtuber们长期沉浸在游戏中、持续挑战游戏的态度，刺激了很多人的心。</p><h2>主角-渚原龙奈（官方视频） </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="主角-渚原龙奈（官方视频）" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qExU8F3gb0g?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@SUZUNANAGIHARA_MP" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>渚原龙奈</strong></a>上传的新原创歌曲是一首犀利的声乐作品，展示了她新的一面。标题“主角”的意思是“英雄”。一个傲慢的女人，在变得激烈的声音中暴露自己的刺，并强烈渴望脱颖而出。除了愤怒之外，他用声音唱出了嫉妒、自信、贪婪、悲伤、严肃等复杂的情感，既有力又细腻。<br />包含了很多伤害的部分，加上听起来多重人声的人声，让歌曲的表现力更加丰富。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.d02zv59swl6z-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.d02zv59swl6z-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.d02zv59swl6z-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.d02zv59swl6z-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.d02zv59swl6z-768x431.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.d02zv59swl6z-jpg.webp 1134w" width="1024" height="575" /></a> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[多重合唱]冰箱里的爱丽丝我试着唱 -Ryuna Nagihara #shorts" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ropMdfFWVcA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>多个合唱的风格本身也被称为“Nagihara Chorus”，并已在许多SHORTS中上传。当声音逐渐增大并且MAIN部分进入最后时，声音的传播非常出色。</p><h2> 【每人21个角色】我们是我试图唱的世界 - We are the World / USA for Africa </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【每人21个角色】我们是我试图唱的世界-我们是世界/美国对非洲" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dGclad63X6Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@akumano_goat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Akuma 的山羊</strong></a>每人表演 21 首合唱。一起唱歌时图片的力量具有非常恶魔的影响。这首歌参加了许多著名歌手，例如Stevie Wonder和Michael Jackson，对每个歌声的细微差别都有一个很好的主意。如果您喜欢西方音乐，则可以获得特征，以便可以在不观看显示名称的情况下击中它。<br />尽管它的复制良好，但它的重点是Akuma山羊的歌，它作为封面具有吸引力，可以将其重现为歌曲。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.ova0qamao3gr-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.ova0qamao3gr-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.ova0qamao3gr-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.ova0qamao3gr-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.ova0qamao3gr-768x431.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/4a5f4cd812a3facb5d9751c9693566c4-kix.ova0qamao3gr-jpg.webp 1137w" width="1024" height="575" /></a></p><p>这是一个窍门，可以从低音到高音中有力地听到。除了模仿个人时唱歌的好方法之外，视频中的每个人的详细信息还为“ Akuma no Goat”，这是很棒的。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="波西米亚狂想曲 -  Queen Cover / Akuma山羊" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qtXG0ulYHpw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在覆盖女王